155
00:05:55,583 --> 00:05:58,208
He's--he's just angry.
Just a phase.

156
00:05:58,250 --> 00:06:01,208
She's all alone. He has
an obligation. He married her.

157
00:06:01,250 --> 00:06:03,333
I love you, Addie,
but you're not really gonna

158
