that he wanted to leave.

166
00:06:19,041 --> 00:06:20,417
But now suddenly,
talking to you--

167
00:06:20,458 --> 00:06:22,041
I'm certain Zach contemplated
leaving long before today.

168
00:06:22,083 --> 00:06:24,834
