Yeah. Actually, no.

218
00:08:13,083 --> 00:08:15,417
Uh, our sheets are ratty,
and there was a sale.

219
00:08:15,458 --> 00:08:17,041
But I-I tried to be romantic.

220
00:08:17,083 --> 00:08:19,083
