No, Sam. I'm not talking
about us.

236
00:08:46,208 --> 00:08:47,667
I was--i am...

237
00:08:47,709 --> 00:08:49,625
Worried about my patient.

238
00:08:49,667 --> 00:08:50,875
Okay?

239
00:08:50,917 --> 00:08:53,000
